name: Winland Electronics
overview: Winland Electronics, Inc. (Winland) designs and manufactures custom electronic controls and assemblies for original equipment manufacturer (OEM) customers, providing services from concept studies through product realization. In addition to the electronic design and manufacturing services Winland provides to OEM customers, the Company has designed and marketed a range of environmental monitoring products to the security industry. Winland designs, produces and distributes products in two segments: Electronic Manufacturing Services (EMS) for OEM customers and proprietary products for the security industry.
